# Quality Gates (kids_math)

> **Canonical source: `AGENTS.md`** — this file provides Cursor-specific details.

## Quality Gates by Mode

### PRO
```bash
npm run lint
npm run check:testids
# If behavior changed: npm run build
# If logic changed: npm run test:unit -- <specific-test-file>
```

### ULTRA
```bash
npm run lint
npm run check:testids
npm run build
npm run test:unit
npm run test:e2e -- <SPECIFIC-spec-files>   # MUST name exact specs
# Then: MCP Playwright visual check (if ANY UI changed)
# Then: npm run test:qa  (full CI suite — must all pass before READY)
```

### MAX
```bash
npm run test:qa   # Full suite, no exceptions
# Then: MCP Playwright visual check (ALWAYS — all changed screens)
# CI is already covered by test:qa
```

